      • setupSequence

        public static TypeController setupSequence(IEvent event,
                           IRace race,
                           IRaceMessageListener listener,
                           long fromTime,
                           long toTime)
        Sets up a subscription for the sequence messages for a given Race.

        The method returns immediately and the data are subsequently sent to a given callback, as they are received.

        The returned type controller should be added to a DataController.

        Parameters:
        event - the event
        race - the race from which to request the data
        listener - the callback to receive the data
        fromTime - the start time
        toTime - the end time
        Returns:
        the type controller
